title: Phenomenal Girl 5
description: A new recruit to the Elite Hands of Justice, the world's premiere cadre of superheroes, Lainey Livingston, who possesses great strength and the ability to fly, falls in love with her trainer, a Reincarnist who cannot die, when they stumble upon a fiendish plot to take over Megolopolis. Original.
author: A.J. Menden
